This is one of the many we have to completely tear down due to improper framing/fasteners, no ledger flashing, failing footers(mainly from water erosion or flawed design) and many other reasons. Unfortunately the decking was screwed down and all the lumber was in good shape so we had to remove about 2600 screws.
